detaileddescription.para: Jean-David Gadina <macmade@eosgarden.com> TARGET_CPU_* These conditionals specify which microprocessor instruction set is being generated. At most one of these is true, the rest are false:
TARGET_RT_* These conditionals specify in which runtime the generated code will run.

listitem.para: TARGET_RT_LITTLE_ENDIAN - Little endian format for integers
TARGET_RT_BIG_ENDIAN - Big endian format for integers
